iations inconsistent with either source. This design enables the model to generate embeddings that are not only statistically plausible but also semantically meaningful, even for classes with minimal or ambiguous visual instances. SPAPA excels in extreme few-shot and zero-shot transfer scenarios, particularly where classes have strong linguistic definitions but limited visual exemplars (e.g., rare species, abstract concepts). By grounding generative imagination in external knowledge, SPAPA moves beyond pure data-driven hallucination toward cognitively informed synthesis, offering a scalable, interpretable, and generalizable solution for low-data representation learning.",
